Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.88,0:00:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Suzuki, selamat pagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.54,0:00:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Azuma, selamat pagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.96,0:00:11.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Boneka itu dari film, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.63,0:00:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar. Makhluk berbulu itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.43,0:00:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau pergi dengan siapa?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.47,0:00:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nabe? Sato?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.68,0:00:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begini…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.31,0:00:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tani.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.35,0:00:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa Tani?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.36,0:00:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami berpacaran.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.86,0:00:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa tak bilang?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.07,0:00:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak sempat.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.32,0:00:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau harus memberitahuku, Bodoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.24,0:00:37.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa? Kapan?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.99,0:00:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baru-baru ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.28,0:00:40.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa maksudmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.41,0:00:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.66,0:00:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siapa yang nembak duluan?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.16,0:00:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begini…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.21,0:00:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pemerasan?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.25,0:00:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dengarkan baik-baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.75,0:00:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Serius?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.92,0:00:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa reaksimu begitu?\NItu baik atau buruk?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.93,0:00:57.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Reaksi yang sangat bagus.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.59,0:01:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku iri sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.43,0:01:01.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa yang terjadi?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.43,0:01:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Astaga. Aku sangat terkejut, sangat lelah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.39,0:01:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.56,0:01:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Omong-omong, kau serius sekali.\NKau mengejutkanku!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.48,0:01:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku? Bukan Tani?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.02,0:01:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika ingin jatuh cinta dengan orang serius,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.07,0:01:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kau juga harus serius.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.45,0:01:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa yang terjadi padamu?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.95,0:01:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika pacarmu seperti Tani,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.03,0:01:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kau tak akan kehilangan kontak\Ndan penasaran dia menghilang,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.91,0:01:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}hanya untuk tahu dia masuk penjara remaja,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.29,0:01:30.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}hal semacam itu, bukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.46,0:01:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukankah ini bagus? Semoga kau bahagia.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.80,0:01:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak mungkin. Itu tak normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.68,0:01:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Taira, kau suka nonton film?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.68,0:01:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku suka film.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.18,0:01:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Penonton di bioskop itu tak bisa ditebak,\Nkayak gacha, jadi aku tak suka pergi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.60,0:01:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gapacho juga bilang begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.14,0:01:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ingin nonton\N"Penyihir dan Makhluk Berbulu".
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.10,0:01:49.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu tak cocok untukmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.23,0:01:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Tapi…\N- Itu suara Suzuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.44,0:01:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Bukannya aku tak mengerti.\N- Berisik sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.23,0:01:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi akhirnya, tergantung orangnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.82,0:01:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku selalu menyukai bajingan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.45,0:02:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semua orang yang membuat\Nkesan pertama bagus adalah bajingan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.91,0:02:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian bahas apa pagi-pagi begini?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.37,0:02:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami bahas bagaimana Azuma\Nbisa miliki hubungan bahagia.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.50,0:02:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menurutku pria jujur tak menarik.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.09,0:02:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia tak bisa diharapkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.05,0:02:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Perempuan suka anak nakal, bukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.30,0:02:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Makin cantik,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.38,0:02:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}makin mereka ingin pacari anak nakal\Nyang dua tahun lebih tua.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.34,0:02:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.26,0:02:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu kenangan SMP-mu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.56,0:02:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi sejujurnya,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.56,0:02:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku bisa memahami
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.85,0:02:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tertarik kepada pria nakal\Ndan berpikir mereka keren.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.44,0:02:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagi pula, kau suka SudaKen, bukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.40,0:02:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pada akhirnya,\Nkau masih memilih berdasarkan hierarki.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.28,0:02:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini bukan soal isi hatinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.37,0:02:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini tentang posisinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.45,0:02:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau hanya ingin bersama seseorang\Ndi peringkat atas.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.20,0:02:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau ingin bangga berada di sisinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.87,0:02:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- SudaKen sangat menawan!\N- Payah sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.17,0:02:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia mulai lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.21,0:02:56.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, Suzuki, boleh bilang begitu?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.96,0:02:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tani sudah datang.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.80,0:03:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat pagi, Tani.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.01,0:03:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Selamat pagi.\N- Konyol sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.77,0:03:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tani, kau dengar perkataan kami?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.14,0:03:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, tapi aku tak peduli\Ndengan hal seremeh itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.48,0:03:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Suzuki manis sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.94,0:03:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akhirnya, "menarik" itu menang.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.98,0:03:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kurasa begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.86,0:03:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa? Apa yang terjadi?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.66,0:03:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka berpacaran.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.91,0:03:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Omong-omong,\Nkenapa semua orang begitu tenang?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.79,0:03:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku menerimanya begitu saja,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.16,0:03:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi ini hal pertama\Nyang terlintas di benakku.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.25,0:03:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa Suzuki merasa Tani cukup baik?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.80,0:03:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi Tani…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.63,0:03:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}SudaKen
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.67,0:03:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}sangat menawan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.72,0:03:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ingin dipimpin.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.01,0:03:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Orang yang lebih tegas akan lebih baik.\N- Cita-cita dan kenyataan Suzuki
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.51,0:03:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- MV dengan pria keren yang terbaik!\N- terlalu berbeda.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.64,0:03:49.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hai.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.60,0:03:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat pagi, Tani.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.10,0:03:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat pagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.35,0:03:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa kau menyapanya\Nseolah kalian teman lama?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.98,0:03:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini dari film itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.94,0:04:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini milikku.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.49,0:04:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan terlalu mesra!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.45,0:04:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mesra?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.61,0:04:05.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Suzuki, di mana fotonya?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.87,0:04:07.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak memotret.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.83,0:04:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia berbohong.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.79,0:04:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Fotonya…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.70,0:04:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tani, diamlah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.29,0:04:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mau lihat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.50,0:04:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tunjukkan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.96,0:04:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Hentikan! Jangan mendekat!\N- Sungguh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.01,0:05:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Panas.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.76,0:05:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mesin penjual otomatis…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.19,0:05:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hai, Taira.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.06,0:06:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hai.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.40,0:06:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, jika kau mencari Reality Gold Strong,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.15,0:06:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}ini kaleng terakhir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.40,0:06:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak minum sampah itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.36,0:06:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi ini lezat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.37,0:06:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, Suzuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.33,0:06:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa kau memilih Tani?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.29,0:06:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau ingin aku memilihmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.21,0:06:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, jangan terlihat begitu takut.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.96,0:06:25.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena kau berbeda
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.76,0:06:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dari anak tipe berenergi tinggi
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.42,0:06:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}seperti Yamada atau Watanabe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.09,0:06:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau sangat pandai baca situasi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.01,0:06:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Atau lebih tepatnya, kau peduli\Ndengan pendapat orang lain.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.89,0:06:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, itu yang kau pikirkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.52,0:06:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Melihatmu memacari orang\Nyang sangat berbeda,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.81,0:06:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku terkejut.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.23,0:06:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sejujurnya, aku selalu sadar diri
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.90,0:06:49.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tentang bagaimana aku sesuaikan diri\Ndengan sekelilingku
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.86,0:06:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan bagaimana orang melihatku,\Nhal-hal seperti itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.91,0:06:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi mungkin karena kepribadianku,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.04,0:07:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}pada keyakinannya, sangat keren.\Norang seperti Tani, yang berpegang
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.17,0:07:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.18,0:07:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika kau ingin dengarkan ceritaku\Ndengan serius,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.89,0:07:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}ini butuh sekitar dua jam. Tak apa-apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.01,0:07:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yang benar saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.52,0:07:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terlalu manis dan aku akan muntah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.73,0:07:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di dekat jendela panas.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.61,0:07:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini dia!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.65,0:07:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku selalu ingin coba ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.16,0:07:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau terkejut?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.82,0:07:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.95,0:07:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benarkah?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.45,0:07:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu yang biasa
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.04,0:07:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dilakukan pasangan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.66,0:07:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku membeli minuman. Mana maumu?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.25,0:07:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yang kuat atau mini?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.63,0:07:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa Reality Gold satu-satunya pilihan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.63,0:07:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.59,0:07:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah kuduga.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.92,0:07:49.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berapa harganya?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.97,0:07:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau tak perlu membayarnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.80,0:07:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, tapi…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.34,0:07:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau sangat kaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.35,0:07:57.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini beracun, terpaksa aku dengarkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.56,0:07:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu… tiga yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.39,0:08:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini bukan kantong plastik.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.14,0:08:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka sangat dekat…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.69,0:08:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Suzuki, kau sudah kembali.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.57,0:08:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.57,0:08:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Minuman bekunya tidak cair-cair.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.69,0:08:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Makanya kupukulkan ke benda keras tadi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.78,0:08:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan bersikap seperti Dewa Penghancur.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.87,0:08:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Suzuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.24,0:08:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada apa lagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.24,0:08:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Coba kulihat PR-mu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.91,0:08:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.08,0:08:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau terlalu sering melakukannya.\NTulis saja sendiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.29,0:08:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tani…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.21,0:08:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.17,0:08:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau tak akan bertanya padaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.34,0:08:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sudah menulisnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.54,0:08:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukankah dia hanya langsung dimanfaatkan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.04,0:08:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi ini sama sekali tak membantumu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.10,0:08:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak apa-apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.35,0:08:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kurasa itu sangat membantu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.65,0:08:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dasar bodoh, baca yang tersirat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.98,0:08:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Suzuki benar-benar melihat Tani apa adanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.20,0:08:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena itu pilihan Suzuki,\Ntak ada yang akan menentangnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.78,0:09:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tak ada yang peduli\Ndengan pendapat orang lain…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.04,0:09:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu rupanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.63,0:09:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kurasa aku mengerti sekarang.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.22,0:09:18.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Perasaan menyebalkan saat seseorang\Nyang tak pernah kau perhatikan
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.26,0:09:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tiba-tiba diakui oleh semua orang,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.93,0:09:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan betapa membosankannya\Nsaat mereka mulai berkompromi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.69,0:09:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sangat peduli dengan perkataan,\Ntindakan, status, dan peringkat orang
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.15,0:09:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}karena aku tak punya standar sendiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.83,0:09:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Taira, ada apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.46,0:09:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Orang yang punya pendapat sendiri
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.33,0:09:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tak terpengaruh perubahan orang lain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.79,0:09:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka pisahkan diri dari orang lain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.01,0:09:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akulah yang terikat hierarki.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.01,0:09:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa? Itu menakutkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.80,0:10:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Taira-Azuma, bagus!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.47,0:10:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan satukan nama kami.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.89,0:10:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian akan pulang bersama?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.56,0:10:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.77,0:10:11.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sampai besok.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.19,0:10:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka berdua pulang bersama\Nsecara terang-terangan,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.45,0:10:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tak peduli pendapat orang lain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.07,0:10:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Entah bagaimana…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.87,0:10:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}mereka berdua sangat mengagumkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.70,0:10:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau hanya berubah saat SMA.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.37,0:10:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Diam.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.71,0:10:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Suzuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.38,0:10:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Misalnya,\Njika kau punya tipe yang kau suka,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.14,0:10:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kurasa bagus untuk mengarah ke sana.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.97,0:10:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi aku tak bisa lakukan apa pun\Nyang bertentangan dengan moralku.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.48,0:10:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bisa memahami
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.61,0:10:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tertarik kepada pria nakal
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.86,0:10:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan berpikir mereka keren.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.53,0:10:59.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu sangat meresahkanmu, bukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.57,0:11:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.74,0:11:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu meresahkan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.70,0:11:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika tak keberatan,\Nkau tak akan mengatakannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.91,0:11:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak keberatan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.50,0:11:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau bohong!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.12,0:11:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tunggu sebentar.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.33,0:11:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa kau sangat bahagia?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.54,0:11:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.51,0:11:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.47,0:11:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tani.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.88,0:11:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada banyak jenis suka.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.97,0:11:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau tahu itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.10,0:11:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, aku tahu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.81,0:11:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yang dianggap "keren"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.73,0:11:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}bisa tentang penampilan,\Nkualitas batin, atau tindakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.06,0:11:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada banyak jenis kekaguman.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.86,0:11:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tahu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.90,0:11:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ekspresimu sekarang manis sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.28,0:11:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau terlalu manis!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.41,0:11:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Orang-orang selalu tertarik\Npada yang mereka anggap keren.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.71,0:11:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tani manis sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.17,0:11:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Manis sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.09,0:12:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Suzuki, apa maksudnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.09,0:12:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tani Kecil manis sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.10,0:12:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak bisa bernapas…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.91,0:12:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau bangun pagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.12,0:12:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tempura membangunkanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.24,0:12:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tempura,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.54,0:12:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kau juga manis sekali hari ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.34,0:12:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bisa memahami
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.84,0:12:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tertarik kepada pria nakal
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.30,0:12:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan berpikir mereka keren.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.97,0:12:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada banyak jenis suka.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.14,0:12:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kubilang aku tak peduli,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.18,0:12:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi menurut Suzuki, keren itu…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.69,0:12:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kuat?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.48,0:13:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, aku…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.99,0:13:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berat sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.08,0:13:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yang benar saja!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.75,0:13:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan halangi aku!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.50,0:13:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Diam!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.96,0:13:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berengsek!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.00,0:13:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ibu, di mana pakaian olahragaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.51,0:13:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak pulang hari ini,\Njadi tak akan makan malam.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.68,0:13:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Serius, jangan mengatakan\Nbanyak hal sekaligus!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.85,0:13:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Beri aku tumpangan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.35,0:13:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berengsek!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.73,0:13:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini cukup jauh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.15,0:13:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan memerintahku!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.70,0:13:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.99,0:13:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cara Suzuki pergi ke sekolah
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.20,0:13:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}sangat karismatik.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.91,0:13:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.08,0:13:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa maksudmu, "Ya, 'kan"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.50,0:13:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Perasaan ada jarak…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.63,0:14:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tani.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.63,0:14:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau tahu siapa yang naik motor tadi?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.51,0:14:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.09,0:14:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Suzuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.68,0:14:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Azu…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.76,0:14:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tani!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.93,0:14:17.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa? Kombinasi macam apa ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.81,0:14:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat pagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.35,0:14:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu kakakmu, bukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.69,0:14:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.73,0:14:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Naik motor itu luar biasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.07,0:14:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Perkenalkan aku padanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.70,0:14:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seleramu buruk sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.49,0:14:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, kan, Tani?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.78,0:14:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan membuatku setuju denganmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.33,0:14:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau lega sekarang?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.67,0:14:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Omong-omong, kau punya saudara?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.38,0:14:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.59,0:14:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Aku tahu, kok.\N- Aku tahu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.97,0:14:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana kalian bisa tahu?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.60,0:14:53.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kakakmu punya pacar?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.81,0:14:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Entahlah. Kalaupun tidak,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.83,0:14:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- tak kurekomendasikan.\N- Pemandangan macam apa ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.69,0:15:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah, ayo pulang!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.53,0:15:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Suzuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.98,0:15:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hari ini giliranku menjaga perpustakaan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.57,0:15:10.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.53,0:15:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa boleh buat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.99,0:15:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nadanya tak terdengar seperti\N"apa boleh buat".
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.47,0:15:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.39,0:15:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Suzuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.85,0:15:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sedang apa di sini?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.31,0:15:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begini…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.27,0:15:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku baru sadar\Nbelum pernah mengunjungi perpustakaan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.98,0:15:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, kumanfaatkan kesempatan ini\Nuntuk melihat-lihat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.11,0:15:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf. Aku seperti penguntit, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.49,0:15:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, aku tak berpikir begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.24,0:15:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benarkah? Syukurlah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.54,0:16:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebenarnya, aku senang sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.08,0:16:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin harusnya kukatakan itu padanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.13,0:16:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi aku tak mau membuatnya\Nmenunggu terlalu lama.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.63,0:16:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Suzuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.47,0:16:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau bosan, kau boleh pulang.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.05,0:16:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga baca buku, tahu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.02,0:16:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, bukan itu maksudku.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.48,0:16:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lupakan ucapanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.40,0:16:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan pinjam buku lalu pulang hari ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.57,0:16:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, kurasa begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.70,0:16:33.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menyebalkan saat orang datang
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.53,0:16:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}cuma untuk menatap, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.57,0:16:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seperti saat teman\Nmengunjungi tempat kerjamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.16,0:16:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rasanya canggung sampai tak tahu
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.87,0:16:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}harus pasang tampang seperti apa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.96,0:16:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rasanya
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.08,0:16:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dia salah paham dengan maksud ucapanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.05,0:16:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Suzuki…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.05,0:16:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Perpustakaan tutup pukul 17.00.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.64,0:17:00.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bisa menunggu?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.54,0:17:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sampai sekarang,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.29,0:17:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tak pernah kuperhatikan
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.88,0:17:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}makna selain harfiah,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.51,0:17:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}perbedaan antara
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.30,0:17:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}yang di permukaan dan di baliknya,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.34,0:17:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}atau apakah ucapanku tersampaikan\Npada orang lain sesuai niatku.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.35,0:17:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak pernah memikirkan itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.27,0:17:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mengekspresikan pikiran
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.19,0:17:47.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}lewat kata-kata,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.81,0:17:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}atau menafsirkan pikiran\Nhanya lewat kata-kata,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.82,0:17:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}takkan pernah sempurna.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.28,0:17:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi kini,\Naku menyadari tiap celah kecilnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.71,0:18:06.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Goma-pon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.58,0:18:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau juga mau pulang, Goma-pon?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.46,0:18:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jelas, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.09,0:18:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau beli sepeda listrik?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.01,0:18:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lucu sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.92,0:18:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan tertawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.51,0:18:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pulanglah sebelum gelap.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.22,0:18:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.26,0:18:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Suzuki, maaf membuatmu menunggu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.77,0:18:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Goma-pon baru saja pergi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.06,0:18:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia naik sepeda…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.81,0:18:32.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wajar, 'kan, naik sepeda?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.82,0:18:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi sepedanya kecil sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.82,0:18:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rodanya sebesar roti kacang merah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.16,0:18:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menurutku itu manis.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.58,0:18:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mulai lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.24,0:18:44.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Suzuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.54,0:18:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa maksudmu "manis"?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.96,0:18:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa maksudku?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.25,0:18:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Contohnya,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.88,0:18:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku mengerti kucing dan panda itu manis.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.63,0:18:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi Pak Goto manis?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.63,0:18:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sungguh tak mengerti.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.05,0:19:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begini…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.01,0:19:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Harus bilang apa selain manis?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.18,0:19:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rasanya hatiku diremas.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.48,0:19:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Disukai.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.69,0:19:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seperti itulah rasanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.24,0:19:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi pria tak pakai kata "manis", 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.41,0:19:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sampai jumpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.00,0:19:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin aku akan lebih sering\Nke perpustakaan
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.33,0:19:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}karena buku ini bagian dari seri.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.54,0:19:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku pernah membacanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.88,0:19:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benarkah?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.96,0:19:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau sudah selesai baca, kita bisa bahas.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.34,0:19:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lain kali, beri tahu aku buku apa\Nyang kau rekomendasikan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.76,0:19:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.68,0:19:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin selera kita beda jauh.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.72,0:19:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi kurasa kita tak perlu\Nsepakat soal segalanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.02,0:19:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana bilangnya, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.44,0:20:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kuharap kita bisa saling mengenal\Npelan-pelan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.28,0:20:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saat kau bilang, "Aku suka ini,"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.91,0:20:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku akan bilang,\N"Oh, rupanya kau suka itu."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.53,0:20:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ingin menjadi seseorang\Nyang sangat memahamimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.58,0:20:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Suzuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.38,0:20:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak bisa jadi pria\Nyang ia anggap keren.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.72,0:20:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.10,0:20:33.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau manis sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.53,0:20:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa itu tersampaikan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.45,0:20:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.86,0:20:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah, sampai jumpa besok.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.12,0:20:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.72,0:21:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu Tani.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.97,0:21:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tani, pagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.35,0:21:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.39,0:21:11.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, Tani.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.77,0:21:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tempo hari aku tanya Suzuki,\N"Kenapa kau pilih Tani?"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.23,0:21:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau tanyakan itu padanya?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.36,0:21:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Katanya kau keren\Nsaat berpegang teguh pada prinsip.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.78,0:21:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Reaksimu dingin amat.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.95,0:21:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa repot-repot memberitahuku?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.74,0:21:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lebih senang dipuji
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.41,0:21:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}di belakang, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.79,0:21:37.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Biasanya orang ingin dengar\Nlangsung dari orangnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.79,0:21:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dibanding pujian yang mungkin\Ncampuran sanjungan,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.34,0:21:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}yang tak kau tahu itu tulus\Natau cuma basa-basi,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.71,0:21:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kata-kata di belakangmu\Nterasa lebih murni, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.88,0:21:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau terlalu paranoid.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.35,0:21:51.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, kau berusaha bikin Tani senang?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.31,0:21:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kebaikanmu unik sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.14,0:21:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Taira, kau orang baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.15,0:22:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah kubilang jangan begitu!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.90,0:22:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku hanya kebetulan lakukan hal\Nyang menguntungkanmu
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.36,0:22:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}saat lampiaskan emosi negatifku.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.78,0:22:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bukan orang baik!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.82,0:22:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Merepotkan sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.91,0:22:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Manga apa itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.08,0:22:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah kubilang, itu buku!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.29,0:22:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau baca buku…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.91,0:22:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aneh.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.17,0:22:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kombinasi aneh.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.62,0:22:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.88,0:22:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nyaris saja aku harus dengar\Ndia membahasnya dua jam.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.21,0:22:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau bikin Tani senang lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.80,0:22:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tani tersenyum. Langka, tuh.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.38,0:22:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.85,0:22:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku frustrasi sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.35,0:22:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Padahal aku lebih menarik!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.89,0:22:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa kau bandingkan dirimu dengannya?
